# NAME

schoolmesh\_posixaccount\_create - Create a posix account for a user

# SYNOPSIS

schoolmesh\_posixaccount\_create *username* *group* *fullname*

# DESCRIPTION

Use this script to create a posix account.
Some checks are done before the creation.

# EXAMPLES

schoolmesh_posixaccount_create john students 'John Doe'

